{"tid":1763146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網購要小心","createTime":"2019-11-30T05:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T05:57:33.000Z","uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7168f2447d75f00a9c1605928b2ec12ddf32898e","tid":1763146,"uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"留學美國的大學生，涉收取藏有丫叉及彈珠的包裹，被控一項企圖管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院提堂，暫毋須答辯，押後明年1月10日再訊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">被告申請保釋被拒</span></span>。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，海關發現相關由美國寄出的可疑包裹後通知警方，有警員其後假扮送貨員前往被告家中送件，並一度拘捕簽收包裹的被告母親，其後再拘捕被告，但控方最終只控告被告一人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n被告趙駿賢（22歲），被控一項企圖管有攻擊性武器罪，指他於今年11月27日，於秀茂坪一個單位內企圖藏有攻擊性武器，即3支彈弓及6包共540顆鋼珠，意圖作非法用途使用。另外，被告亦涉及另一宗案件，指他於今年11月11日，於灣仔灣仔襲警及管有攻擊性武器，被告於該案獲准保釋，案件押後明年1月21日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AB%E5%8F%89-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%96%AC%E8%A3%9D%E9%80%81%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%25B9%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%25AB%25E5%258F%2589-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2596%25AC%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf%2FvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=bee0a236\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%25B9%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%25AB%25E5%258F%2589-%25